Subject: Appliance disk space warning.
Description:
Seeing the following message after logging in:



Your appliance is running low on disk space, there is 15.56 gb free available from 49.09 gb (32%). EPP Server functionality and performance may be severely affected. Use Audit Log Backup to reduce the logs stored in the database, delete older system and audit log backups, and tune policies to reduce incoming log count. For further assistance contact Support.
Solution_Comment__c: disk space cleared + php logs limit set
